{"tid":109426,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[critical thinking] separation of power manifested?","createTime":"2017-02-06T03:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T06:36:01.000Z","uid":48213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a774f7cd9da9bf32d55a419466762e7bee862a54","tid":109426,"uid":48213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T03:08:16.000Z","msg":"[Separation of power manifested in court halting travel ban?]<br />\n<br />\n岩岩先法院ban鳩左trump仔唔比7個國家既人入境既行政命令：<br />\nA federal appeals court early Sunday morning denied the US government's emergency request to resume President Donald Trump's travel ban.<br />\n<br />\n個法官robart 仔又講左啲咩呢：<br />\n&quot;have met their burden of demonstrating that they face immediate and irreparable injury as a result of the signing and implementation of the executive order&quot;<br />\n<br />\n暫時事態發展係：<br />\nSince the federal appeals court rejected a request to immediately reinstate the travel ban, lawyers for Washington state and Minnesota have until 3:59 a.m. ET Monday to file legal papers, and the Justice Department lawyers have until 6 p.m. ET Monday evening to reply. <br />\n就咁睇就仲有待ruling/ hearing (我得一個source, 有錯請屌)<br />\n<br />\n迷思：<br />\n究竟呢單野係體現緊三權分立既pro定con? 咁樣比法院ban其實變相降低緊各樣行政上execution efficiency, 小則喺入境製造混亂，前線人員無所適從，大則遲啲頒佈其他行政命令嗰陣，啲judge已經accustomed to banning trump's order , 搞到trump仔乜都execute唔到？明明係選民授權既president應唔應該override任命番黎既judge呢？<br />\n<br />\n備註：個judge之前告鳩差佬殺黑人既前科controversy<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/f6oqya8g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ff6oqya8g&h=47b20673&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebd42ad593e1d25985f49661f4ce383abb8f09bd","tid":109426,"uid":48213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T03:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd128665bd108cfdcf644ea3ae4a98624415d9a9","tid":109426,"uid":48213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB